      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'pre-owned.' This car is in showroom condition, having been meticulously garaged and climate-controlled since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, entirely free from swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no creasing or wear on the bolsters, and the original factory scent still lingers. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity surround-sound system to the advanced navigation interface, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by brand-certified technicians using OEM parts. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
